{"tid":1983752,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"周迅18歲人體模特油彩畫曝光，一幅作品價值近2百萬","createTime":"2020-04-22T04:39:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T05:40:35.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a9579e073f1cff4359b10b7fdb85c43e96c67bfa","tid":1983752,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T04:39:04.000Z","msg":"一直以來，周迅都是大家心中最有靈氣的女演員，早年和徐靜蕾、趙薇以及章子怡並稱&ldquo;四大花旦&rdquo;，相繼取得近10個影后殊榮，近日網上卻傳出她在踏上影后之路之前，曾擔任人體模特兒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.sina.com/spider2020421/562/w640h722/20200421/cc72-isqivxf5929580.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.sina.com%2Fspider2020421%2F562%2Fw640h722%2F20200421%2Fcc72-isqivxf5929580.jpg&h=b88070cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4月21日凌晨，有媒體曝出一組周迅18歲時的人像油畫，並透露其如今都價值不菲，其中有一張造型還極其大膽，藝術感極強。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n畫中的長相酷似周迅的少女長髮飄飄、稚嫩的面龐笑容淺淺，上身赤裸抱着一個陶罐，下身也纏繞着飛揚的絲巾，雖然上身未着寸縷，反而讓人感覺到一股純真氣息，極具藝術性。"},{"pid":"b50bc7c48847dd97fae2b49dbd01341dc9cbe8fe","tid":1983752,"uid":79142,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T04:39:50.000Z","msg":"樓主老母18歲人體模特油彩畫曝光，一幅作品價值近廿蚊"},{"pid":"309ba0cecd84770daa4cd24313a6d46316f34a51","tid":1983752,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T05:12:31.000Z","msg":"支那支"},{"pid":"a9262a73b3048b0dfc92792b3b4d6be248228acb","tid":1983752,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T05:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/18/152502_b1013596d77a467181d30f9cb115edc4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F18%2F152502_b1013596d77a467181d30f9cb115edc4.png&h=de8994a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65b2ce9a8158b522e5c6f067d7f1efd579dc77ac","tid":1983752,"uid":115250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T05:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OeY3CWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOeY3CWu.jpg&h=c61bdcfa&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}